Author: designer#4893
Content: In fact, the argument between the on-and-off-chain camp is so hot because it touches on the essential question of "what is Bitcoin?" If mainstream media, the public and on-chain advocates focus on the value of implementing low-cost payments, which was also the original purpose of bitcoin, those who prefer off-chain methods consider Bitcoin to be the "safe registry" invented by mankind.
